data.description: Lets make this home yours and receive $2,500 Seller Concessions to assist Buyer with closing costs. This spacious four-bedroom two-bathroom home, conveniently located near schools and parks and minutes away from Downtown Midlothian. The spacious living room boasts abundant natural light, perfect for for both relaxing in front of the fireplace or for entertaining guests. Each bedroom is generously sized and can be easily customized to fit your personal style. The expansive yard offers endless possibilities for outdoor activities from gardening to hosting summer barbecues. This home presents an excellent opportunity for creating lasting memories. Don't miss out on the chance to make it your own! NO HOA!
